🩺 HealthAI Coach

HealthAI Coach is an AI-powered health and nutrition assistant that helps users track their health, calories, hydration, and receive personalized recommendations.

🚀 How I Built This Project
Step 1: Idea

I wanted to create a platform where users can:

Store personal and medical information.
Track calories and water intake.
Receive AI-powered health recommendations.
Monitor their daily health progress.
Step 2: No-Code Development
Used Base44 as the development platform.
Described features using natural language prompts.
Base44 generated the UI and application structure automatically.
Step 3: Main Features Implemented
User profile setup
Health dashboard
Daily calorie tracker
Water intake tracker
Personalized nutrition recommendations
Light and dark mode support
Mobile-responsive interface
Step 4: Design

Focused on:

Clean and modern interface
Mobile-first design
Easy navigation
User-friendly dashboard
Step 5: Testing
Tested responsiveness on different screen sizes.
Verified navigation and dashboard functionality.
Improved layout and usability through iterations.
Step 6: Future Enhancements
Food image recognition
AI chatbot
Meal planner
Exercise tracker
Health report generation
Wearable device integration
